  <brief_title>Assessing Foot Injuries in Infantry Recruits Wearing Different Boots</brief_title>
  <official_title>Assessing Foot Injuries in Infantry Recruits Wearing Different Boots, a Prospective Randomized Study</official_title>
  <sponsors>
